title: Council celebrates success of 2015 Monash University Casey Challenge (Casey City Council)
text: ( Source : Casey City Council ) Issued Monday 26 October 2015 Waverley Christian College were crowned the 2015 Monash University Casey Challenge winners, as the program wrapped up with a final presentation night on Wednesday 14 October 2015.
